A Nigerian lady identified as Cynthia Anyisia, has taken to social media to advise men to marry women who can at least afford to pay electricity bill. Cynthia on a popular Facebook group, gave this advice Yesterday, September 9, 2020.According to her, Nigerian men when getting married, should marry a lady who can afford to pay for electricity bill without needing assistant, unlike those who would let power supply to be disconnected and wait for the husband to return so they could tell him “honey they have cut our light”. She Wrote; “Marry a woman that can at least pay for Nepa bill. Not the one that will say honey they have cut our light”  Source